  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1295148/" class="title-link">本书的脉络</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1295148"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/net2/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1436123-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/net2/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">大而化之</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-02-01"
      class="main-meta">2008-02-01 15:45:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1295148_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      应该说，这本书的脉络还是很一致的——但并不是很清晰的。可能由于李普曼本身以专栏作家出名，这本书似乎表现出了他缺乏长篇写作的驾驭能力。的确，书中的每一句话都很深刻并有着悠远的含蓄暗示。可是，书中的脉络就被隐藏在这些段落和语句中了。看看李普特为了论证联邦宪...

